1. download the graphics.h and winbgim.h
2. go to your Dev-Cpp folder in your x86 program files, then open MINGW64, then open the include folder
3. paste them in your include folder
4. then on the previous MINGW64 folder, find your lib folder and open
5. download the libbgi.a
6. paste in your lib folder
7. open dev c++
8. create project
9. click project --> project options --> parameters
10. paste the next lines on your linker list:
    -lbgi
    -luser32
    -lgdi32
    -lcomdlg32
    -luuid
    -loleaut32
    -lole32
11. run the program
